caption.title: Metabolomic impact of AGPAT1 and AGPAT2 depletion in uninfected mosquitoes as measured by ion intensity.
caption.p: Two days post dsRNA injection against AGPAT1 (dsAGPAT1) or control (dsControl), mosquitoes were orally infected with DENV at 10 7 pfu/ml. Metabolomic analyses were performed at 2 and 7 dpi. Normalized ion intensity was calculated after total ion chromatography normalization and auto scaling from three replicates. Conditions with significantly regulated metabolites (p-value <0.05 and |log2 fold change| >1) were indicated with an asterisk.
